Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:39.68,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,what truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:43.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I’ll come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:54.61,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I see that bright light.
